# qb-linq tests

- Framework: **GoogleTest**; target **`qb_linq_tests`**.
- New behaviour or fixes: add/extend cases in **`tests/`** (`linq_*_test.cpp` naming).
- Include **`#include <qb/linq.h>`** (or focused headers only if testing internals—prefer public API).
- Run **`ctest --output-on-failure`** or the test binary after changes.
